              <div style="font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:26px;font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;letter-spacing:0.02em;line-height:1.2;">Papeterie Messenger Supplier Ltd</div>
              <div style="width:48px;height:2px;background:#daa13c;margin:14px auto 0;"></div>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td style="padding:36px 40px 28px;">
              <h2 style="font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:400;color:#1e3a8a;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:0.01em;">Hello, {{staffName}}</h2>
              <p style="font-size:15px;color:#374151;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 14px;">You have been granted system access for <strong style="color:#1e3a8a;">{{businessName}}</strong>. Use the credentials below to log in to your account.</p>

              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="background:#f0f6ff;border:1px solid #bfdbfe;border-radius:4px;margin:24px 0;">
                <tr><td style="padding:20px 24px;">
                  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="font-size:13px;color:#64748b;padding:5px 0;width:140px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.06em;">Login URL</td>
                      <td style="font-size:13px;color:#2563eb;padding:5px 0;"><a href="https://system.izubagen.rw" style="color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">https://system.izubagen.rw</a></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr><td colspan="2" style="height:1px;background:#bfdbfe;padding:0;font-size:0;"></td></tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td style="font-size:13px;color:#64748b;padding:5px 0;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.06em;">Email</td>
                      <td style="font-size:13px;color:#1e3a8a;padding:5px 0;">{{email}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr><td colspan="2" style="height:1px;background:#bfdbfe;padding:0;font-size:0;"></td></tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td style="font-size:13px;color:#64748b;padding:5px 0;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.06em;">Temp. Password</td>
                      <td style="font-size:13px;color:#1e3a8a;padding:5px 0;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.04em;">{{password}}</td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                </td></tr>
              </table>

              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="margin:8px 0 20px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background:#1e3a8a;border-radius:3px;">
                    <a href="https://system.izubagen.rw" style="display:inline-block;padding:13px 32px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.05em;text-transform:uppercase;">Log In Now</a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="border-left:3px solid #daa13c;background:#fffbeb;border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;margin:20px 0;">
                <tr><td style="padding:12px 16px;font-size:13px;color:#92400e;line-height:1.5;">
                  <strong>Important:</strong> Please log in and update your password immediately for security purposes.
                </td></tr>
              </table>

              <p style="font-size:14px;color:#64748b;line-height:1.6;margin:0;">If you experience any issues, please contact your business administrator.</p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td style="background:#f8fafc;border-top:3px solid #daa13c;padding:24px 40px;text-align:center;">
              <p style="font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#1e3a8a;margin:0 0 6px;letter-spacing:0.02em;">Papeterie Messenger Supplier Ltd</p>
              <p style="font-size:12px;color:#64748b;margin:0 0 4px;">Kigali, Rwanda &nbsp;|&nbsp; +250 784 544 729 &nbsp;|&nbsp; papemessenger@gmail.com</p>
              <p style="font-size:11px;color:#94a3b8;margin:12px 0 0;">&copy; {{year}} Papeterie Messenger Supplier Ltd. All rights reserved.</p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
